727
00:55:35,583 --> 00:55:36,918
Into a paper bag.

728
00:55:38,419 --> 00:55:42,423
A great moment of civic compromise.

729
00:55:42,507 --> 00:55:46,427
That small wrinkled-ass paper bag...

730
00:55:46,511 --> 00:55:49,639
Allowed the corner boys
to have their drink in peace,

731
00:55:50,598 --> 00:55:52,266
and it gave us permission...

732
00:55:53,142 --> 00:55:56,103
To go and do police work.

733
00:55:58,147 --> 00:56:02,026
The kind of police work
that's actually worth the effort.

734
00:56:03,945 --> 00:56:08,115
That's worth actually...
Taking a bullet for.

735
00:56:10,368 --> 00:56:14,956
Dozerman,
he got shot last night trying to buy...

736
00:56:15,039 --> 00:56:17,041
Three vials.

737
00:56:17,124 --> 00:56:18,459
Three!

738
00:56:28,052 --> 00:56:32,682
There's never been a paper bag for drugs...

739
00:56:40,481 --> 00:56:42,066
Until now.

740
00:56:49,574 --> 00:56:51,993
If we ain't doing hand-to-hands,
then what the fuck?

741
00:56:53,786 --> 00:56:55,580
And the shit with the bag?

742
00:56:55,663 --> 00:56:57,665
What the fuck is that?

